00:53:49,860 --> 00:53:51,089
Hentikan.

935
00:53:51,389 --> 00:53:54,330
Kamu duduk di sisi kanan? Pasti kamu tidak kidal.

936
00:53:54,330 --> 00:53:55,400
Maaf?

937
00:53:55,529 --> 00:53:57,900
- Kamu hakim di sisi kanan.
- Hentikan.

938
00:53:57,900 --> 00:54:00,069
Benar.

939
00:54:01,469 --> 00:54:02,940
- Silakan.
- Terima kasih.

940
00:54:06,440 --> 00:54:09,440
Makgeolli lebih nikmat jika diminum bersama-sama.

941
00:54:09,440 --> 00:54:12,310
Benar. Minumlah.

942
00:54:14,319 --> 00:54:15,679
Bersulang.

943
00:54:15,679 --> 00:54:16,949
- Bersulang.
- Bersulang.

944
00:54:17,589 --> 00:54:20,089
Kalian membawa banyak makanan.

